@startuml 订单事件中心发布与消费流程
!include <C4/C4_Container>
!include <C4/C4_Context>

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor #FEFEFE
    BorderColor #555555
}

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #FEFEFE
    BorderColor #555555
}

' Colors
!define SERVICE_COLOR #E8F5E9
!define MQ_COLOR #FFF3E0
!define DB_COLOR #E3F2FD
!define EXT_COLOR #FCE4EC

title 订单事件中心 — 事件发布与消费流程

' ========== 参与者 ==========

actor "OrderService" as OrderService #SERVICE_COLOR
participant "EventPublisher\n(EventPublisherImpl)" as EventPublisher #SERVICE_COLOR
collections "RocketMQ\nORDER_EVENT" as MQ #MQ_COLOR
database "事件存储\n(event_store)" as EventStore #DB_COLOR
participant "EventRouter\n(事件路由器)" as EventRouter #SERVICE_COLOR
participant "EventDeliveryLog\n(delivery_log)" as DeliveryLog #DB_COLOR

' ========== 消费者 ==========
participant "物流消费者\n(logistics-consumer)" as LogisticsConsumer #SERVICE_COLOR
participant "积分消费者\n(points-consumer)" as PointsConsumer #SERVICE_COLOR
participant "营销消费者\n(marketing-consumer)" as MarketingConsumer #SERVICE_COLOR
participant "Webhook投递\n(webhook-dispatcher)" as WebhookDispatcher #SERVICE_COLOR
actor "外部系统\n(第三方回调URL)" as ExternalSystem #EXT_COLOR

' ========== 第 1 阶段：事件发布 ==========

== 阶段 1：事务消息事件发布 ==

OrderService -> EventPublisher: publish(orderPaidEvent)
activate EventPublisher

EventPublisher -> EventPublisher: ① 生成 eventId (UUID)
EventPublisher -> EventPublisher: ② 填充元数据\n(source/timestamp/traceId)
EventPublisher -> EventStore: ③ 写入 event_store\n(status=PENDING)
activate EventStore
EventStore --> EventPublisher: OK
deactivate EventStore

EventPublisher -> MQ: ④ 发送 RocketMQ 事务半消息
activate MQ
MQ --> EventPublisher: 半消息发送成功

EventPublisher -> OrderService: ⑤ 执行本地事务\n（更新订单状态等）
OrderService --> EventPublisher: 本地事务成功

EventPublisher -> MQ: ⑥ 提交半消息 → 消费者可见
deactivate MQ

EventPublisher -> EventStore: ⑦ 更新 event_store\n(status=PUBLISHED)
activate EventStore
EventStore --> EventPublisher: OK
deactivate EventStore

deactivate EventPublisher

note right #FEFEFE
  事务消息确保：
  事件不丢失 = 半消息先到 MQ
  事件不早于业务 = 本地事务成功后才提交
  事务回查 = Broker 回调 checkLocalTransaction
end note

' ========== 第 2 阶段：事件路由与消费 ==========

== 阶段 2：事件路由与消费 ==

MQ -> EventRouter: 消费 ORDER_EVENT 消息
activate EventRouter

EventRouter -> EventRouter: ① 解析消息 Header\n(eventType/bizScope/source)
EventRouter -> EventRouter: ② 查询 event_subscription\n匹配订阅规则
EventRouter -> EventRouter: ③ 通配匹配 + 业务线过滤\n+ SpEL条件过滤

' ====== 并行分发给多个消费者 ======

' --- 物流消费者 ---
EventRouter -> LogisticsConsumer: ④ 分发给匹配的消费者
activate LogisticsConsumer
LogisticsConsumer -> LogisticsConsumer: 处理物流单创建
LogisticsConsumer -> DeliveryLog: 记录 SUCCESS
activate DeliveryLog
DeliveryLog --> LogisticsConsumer: OK
deactivate DeliveryLog
LogisticsConsumer --> EventRouter: 消费完成
deactivate LogisticsConsumer

' --- 积分消费者 ---
EventRouter -> PointsConsumer: ④ 分发给积分消费者
activate PointsConsumer
PointsConsumer -> PointsConsumer: 处理积分赠送
PointsConsumer -> DeliveryLog: 记录 SUCCESS
activate DeliveryLog
DeliveryLog --> PointsConsumer: OK
deactivate DeliveryLog
PointsConsumer --> EventRouter: 消费完成
deactivate PointsConsumer

' --- 营销消费者 ---
EventRouter -> MarketingConsumer: ④ 分发给营销消费者
activate MarketingConsumer
MarketingConsumer -> MarketingConsumer: 更新营销数据
MarketingConsumer -> DeliveryLog: 记录 SUCCESS
activate DeliveryLog
DeliveryLog --> MarketingConsumer: OK
deactivate DeliveryLog
MarketingConsumer --> EventRouter: 消费完成
deactivate MarketingConsumer

' --- Webhook 投递 ---
EventRouter -> WebhookDispatcher: ④ 分发给 Webhook 投递
activate WebhookDispatcher

WebhookDispatcher -> WebhookDispatcher: 查询 event_subscription\n(notify_url 非空)
WebhookDispatcher -> WebhookDispatcher: HMAC-SHA256 签名
WebhookDispatcher -> ExternalSystem: HTTP POST 事件回调
activate ExternalSystem

alt 2xx 成功
    ExternalSystem --> WebhookDispatcher: 200 OK
    WebhookDispatcher -> DeliveryLog: 记录 SUCCESS
else 非 2xx 或超时
    ExternalSystem --> WebhookDispatcher: 5xx / 超时
    WebhookDispatcher -> WebhookDispatcher: 指数退避重试\n(1s→2s→4s→...→8m)

    alt 重试成功
        ExternalSystem --> WebhookDispatcher: 200 OK
        WebhookDispatcher -> DeliveryLog: 记录 SUCCESS (attempt=N)
    else 超过最大重试次数
        WebhookDispatcher -> MQ: 投递 DLQ (死信队列)
        WebhookDispatcher -> DeliveryLog: 记录 DLQ
        MQ -> Monitor: DLQ 深度 > 100 → P1 告警
    end
end

deactivate ExternalSystem
WebhookDispatcher --> EventRouter: 投递完成
deactivate WebhookDispatcher

deactivate EventRouter

note right #FEFEFE
  Webhook 使用 ADR-033 的投递引擎：
  - HMAC-SHA256 签名验证
  - 指数退避 1s→2s→4s→...→8m
  - 最多 10 次重试
  - DLQ 兜底 + 告警
end note

' ========== 第 3 阶段：可观测性 ==========

== 阶段 3：可观测性采集 ==

Participant "Prometheus\n(指标聚合)" as Prometheus #DB_COLOR
Participant "Grafana\n(集成健康大盘)" as Grafana #DB_COLOR

EventPublisher -> Prometheus: omplatform_integration_event_published_total\n{event_type="order.paid", status="success"}
LogisticsConsumer -> Prometheus: omplatform_integration_event_consumed_total\n{consumer_group="logistics", status="success"}
LogisticsConsumer -> Prometheus: omplatform_integration_event_consume_duration\n{consumer_group="logistics"}
MQ -> Prometheus: omplatform_integration_event_backlog\n{consumer_group="logistics"}

Prometheus -> Grafana: 聚合指标
Grafana -> Grafana: 集成健康大盘渲染\n(总览看板 / API 看板 / 事件看板)

note right #FEFEFE
  集成可观测性 3 个看板：
  ① 集成总览 — 全局健康评分 + Top 趋势
  ② API 详情 — 按 AppKey 维度 QPS/延迟/错误率
  ③ 事件详情 — 按事件类型/消费者组维度堆积/延迟
end note

@enduml
